{%- comment -%}
  NMN+ product story — Seed-style conversion architecture, full-bleed bands.
  Band order mirrors seed.com/daily-synbiotic: benefit tiles (4.2) → capsule /
  disclosure explainer (4.3) → practice timeline → supplement facts (4.4) →
  comparison (4.5) → delivery (4.6) → standards (4.7) → FAQ (4.8) → sticky
  CTA (4.9). The hero (4.1: gallery / price / add-to-cart) is Shopify's
  buy-box section rendered above this one via templates/product.nmn.json.
  All claims are constrained to the real product label. No reviews, clinical
  trials, guarantees, kits, or refill tiers are invented.
{%- endcomment -%}

