        <p>NMN (nicotinamide mononucleotide), trans-resveratrol, quercetin, the active forms of vitamins B6, B12 and folate, and BioPerine black-pepper extract — in a plant-based HPMC capsule. Every dose is printed in full on the label, and the other ingredients (microcrystalline cellulose, magnesium stearate, silicon dioxide, and the vegetable capsule) are disclosed too. No proprietary blends. The exact milligrams are in the formula table above and on each batch's Certificate of Analysis.</p>
